# Customizing Large Language Models

<img src="https://images.code.org/1cd0ec71458414495502b9598efd2028-image-1639773441510.37.01 PM.png" alt="AI bot" style="border-radius:40px; float: right; padding-right: 20px; height: 150px; clear: both; margin: 0 20px 20px 0;">

#### Now that you have learned more about what Generative AI is, let's dive into how to customize large language models.

#### This unit is designed to deepen students' understanding of how text-based generative AI models function and how they can be customized for specific tasks. Students will explore how system prompts and retrieval methods influence the behavior of AI models, allowing them to generate more accurate and relevant responses. Then, students will learn user-centered design strategies to design even more specialized chatbots.

#### By the end of this unit, students will have the skills to create a chatbot that addresses a personally relevant issue or an issue in their community.

## **In this lesson you will:** 
- #### Review the content of each lesson in the Customizing Large Language Models Unit
- #### Preview activities in the lessons


### **Suggested time:** 60 minutes


